SIMPLE: underline
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Underline
<hw>Un`der*line"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>To
mark a line below, as words; to underscore.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>To influence secretly.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>Sir H. Wotton.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>Emphasize or call attention to; highlight; <as>as,
Long waits at the emergency room <ex>underline</ex> the need for a
larger hospital</as>.</def> <q>.</q>⟦br⟧
[<source>JG</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Underling</ent>⟦br⟧
